# Day_03
Prblm statement :  The "Healthy Kids" Nutrition & Growth Analysis 
Focuses on the relationship between a child's dietary habits and their physical development, 
using a realistic, though fictional, dataset.

Given a dataset consist of 200 children records with the following attributes, 
child_ID | Age_Months | Gender | Height | Weight | Daily_Fruit_servings | Daily_Veggie_servings | Daily_sugar_Drinks | Screen Time hours | Region | BMI | Health_Status
